-- [[ ü•ä ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏ï‡∏µ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏î‡∏±‡∏ö 100% (MARU SPEED) ]]
task.spawn(function()
    while true do
        -- ‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏£‡πá‡∏ß‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏á‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ (0.01 ‡∏Ñ‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏±‡∏î‡πÜ ‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏î‡∏±‡∏ö 100%)
        task.wait(0.01) 
        
        if Options.AutoFarmToggle.Value then
            pcall(function()
                local Char = LP.Character
                local Tool = Char:FindFirstChildOfClass("Tool")
                
                if Tool then
                    -- [ üíé 100% SPEED METHOD ]
                    -- ‡∏™‡∏±‡πà‡∏á‡∏ï‡∏µ‡∏ú‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô Tool ‡πÇ‡∏î‡∏¢‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏á
                    Tool:Activate()
                    
                    -- ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ VirtualInputManager ‡πÄ‡∏ö‡∏¥‡πâ‡∏•‡∏î‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏°‡∏à‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏û‡∏¥‡πÄ‡∏®‡∏©
                    -- (‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏ó‡∏≥‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡∏ï‡∏µ‡πÑ‡∏ß‡∏Å‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤‡∏õ‡∏Å‡∏ï‡∏¥ 2 ‡πÄ‡∏ó‡πà‡∏≤)
                    VIM:SendMouseButtonEvent(0, 0, 0, true, game, 1)
                    VIM:SendMouseButtonEvent(0, 0, 0, false, game, 1)
                    
                    -- ‡πÅ‡∏ñ‡∏°‡∏£‡∏∞‡∏ö‡∏ö‡πÇ‡∏à‡∏°‡∏ï‡∏µ‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏û‡∏¥‡πÄ‡∏®‡∏© (‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏µ‡πÇ‡∏°‡∏î‡∏π‡∏•‡πÇ‡∏à‡∏°‡∏ï‡∏µ‡πÉ‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏Å‡∏°)
                    local CombatRemote = game:GetService("ReplicatedStorage"):FindFirstChild("RigControllerEvent") or game:GetService("ReplicatedStorage"):FindFirstChild("CombatEvent")
                    if CombatRemote then
                        CombatRemote:FireServer()
                    end
                end
            end)
        end
    end
end)
